msgstr "विद्यमानं पुस्तकालयं उद्घाटयति"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open Recent"
msgstr "Open Recent इति"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a recently used library"
msgstr "सद्यः प्रयुक्तं पुस्तकालयं उद्घाटयन्तु"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>रक्षतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the library"
msgstr "पुस्तकालयं रक्षति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Save As</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>यथा रक्षतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the library under a new name"
msgstr "पुस्तकालयं नूतननाम्ना रक्षति"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Symbol"
msgstr "प्रतीकं रक्षतु"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Save the symbol being edited</action></simpara> <simpara>If "
"the symbol being edited was selected from the library, saving will update "
"that symbol. If it is a new symbol, it will be appended to the library and "
"subsequent saves will append another new symbol to the library. </simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>सम्पादितं चिह्नं रक्षतु</action></simpara> <simpara>यदि सम्पादितं "
"चिह्नं पुस्तकालयात् चयनितम् आसीत् तर्हि रक्षणं तत् चिह्नं अद्यतनं करिष्यति । यदि नूतनं चिह्नं "
"भवति तर्हि पुस्तकालये संलग्नं भविष्यति तदनन्तरं रक्षणं पुस्तकालये अन्यत् नूतनं चिह्नं योजयिष्यति । "
"</simpara> इति"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Symbol as New"
msgstr "Symbol इत्येतत् New इति रक्षन्तु"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Save the symbol being edited as a new symbol</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>When a symbol is saved as new it will be appended to the "
"library regardless of it having originally been selected from the library "
"for editing. Subsequent saves will append another new symbol to the library. "
"</simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>सम्पादितं चिह्नं नूतनचिह्नरूपेण रक्षतु</action></simpara> "
"<simpara>यदा चिह्नं नूतनरूपेण रक्षितं भवति तदा तत् पुस्तकालयात् मूलतः चयनितं न कृत्वा "
"पुस्तकालये संलग्नं भविष्यति सम्पादनार्थम् । अनन्तरं रक्षणं पुस्तकालये अन्यत् नूतनं चिह्नं योजयिष्यति "
"। </simpara> इति"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import Library"
msgstr "आयात पुस्तकालय"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import a library appending the contained symbols into the current library"
msgstr "वर्तमानपुस्तकालये समाविष्टानि चिह्नानि योजयित्वा पुस्तकालयं आयातयन्तु"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>बन्दं कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close the library"
msgstr "पुस्तकालयं पिधाय"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>निर्गम</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quits &symboleditor;"
msgstr "त्यजति &symboleditor;"

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "सम्पादन मेनू इति"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&symboleditor; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu items, for "
"more information read the sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-edit\">Edit Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&प्रतीकसम्पादक; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सम्पादयतु</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं "
"&kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
